tool_description: The style transfer capability can transform the style of the input image, so that the visual style of the image such as color and brush strokes can be transformed.
name: Style migration
title: Style migration

api_list.name: Style migration

required_parameters.name: major
required_parameters.description:
Content image.
- **Image format**: `JPEG` `JPG` `PNG` `BMP`
- **Image size**: No more than 3 MB.
- **Image resolution**: Less than 1200x1200px.
- The images must all be RGB 3-channel.
